title: Epistle to the Apostle I (Simple Earthling Edit)
description:
It took more trimming than can be done in YouTube, but LightWorks let me fix the sound some. Here is the transmission from the dirty antenna with as much of the noise removed from the signal I could manage.

Pageau commented on the Briss'd Edition, but seemed confused. 
Briss'd Edition includes info card for the extra sources, and a link to the original livestream:
Briss'd Edition:  /watch?v=77GfgT0kudI

TIMESTAMPS:
06:26 actual start
07:33 I know who you are
08:33 uninterpreted
09:33 squirt is a weapon
11:12 uninterpreted
12:33 Chapter II
14:04 Fringe Nexus Frontier
14:33 PB4J
15:33 Apocalypse

Here's a Discord for people who don't hate me: https://discord.gg/W8tnFw5t9p
Here's a Patreon for people who want to encourage me: https://www.patreon.com/grimgriz

https://grimgriz.substack.com/
